                            <p class="text-justify">Crime rates in Singapore are meagre compared to other destinations because the country is heavily policed. Strong punishments are imposed on those who break the laws and attempt crimes. Singapore is a favourite spot for food lovers where they will enjoy diverse and innovative cuisines. The cuisines are of a high standard and affordable budget. </p>

                            <p class="text-justify">Solo backpackers will never feel lonely in this country. Take a stroll through the Bay East Garden to enjoy the vibrant plant life and escape the city bustle for a moment. You can head towards the Cloud Forest Dome to see the world's tallest indoor waterfall. Visit the Singapore zoo to encounter various species. The Orchard Road area is a great place for shopaholics. Try visiting Chinatown during your stay. </p>

